#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:1
msgid "E0014"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:3
msgid "Warning name: `alert` or `alert_<category>`"
msgstr "警告名称：`alert` 或 `alert_<category>`"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:5
msgid ""
"Alert warnings are emitted when code uses an API that carries an alert, "
"for example through `#alert`, [`#internal`](../attributes.md#internal-"
"attribute), or a visibility-change annotation. The alert category is "
"chosen by the API provider, so the warning name can be `alert` for all "
"alerts or `alert_<category>` for one category."
msgstr ""
"当代码使用了带有 alert 的 API 时会发出 alert 警告，例如通过 `#alert`、"
"[`#internal`](../attributes.md#internal-attribute) 或可见性变更标注产生的 "
"alert。Alert 的类别由 API 提供者选择，因此警告名称可以是用于所有 alert 的 "
"`alert`，也可以是用于某一类别的 `alert_<category>`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:10
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:12
msgid ""
"The provider module marks `experimental` as internal, and the importing "
"module calls it:"
msgstr ""
"provider 模块将 `experimental` 标记为 internal，导入它的模块随后调用了"
"它："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:15
#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:30
msgid "provider/top.mbt"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:15
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"#internal(experimental, \"use stable instead\")\n"
"pub fn experimental() -> Int {\n"
"  1\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:20
#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:35
msgid "top.mbt"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:20
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  inspect(@provider.experimental(), content=\"1\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:25
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "修改建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:27
msgid ""
"Read the alert category and message, then follow the guidance for that "
"specific API. Different alert categories can mean different things: an "
"API may be experimental, deprecated, visibility-changing, unsafe, not "
"total, or carry a provider-defined meaning."
msgstr ""
"请阅读 alert 的类别和消息，然后按照该 API 的具体指引处理。不同 alert 类别的含"
"义可能不同：API 可能是实验性的、已弃用的、即将改变可见性的、不安全的、非全函"
"数的，或者带有提供者自定义的含义。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:32
msgid "In this example, the provider asks callers to use the stable API instead:"
msgstr "在这个示例中，provider 要求调用方改用稳定 API："

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:30
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"pub fn stable() -> Int {\n"
"  1\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E0014.md:35
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"test {\n"
"  inspect(@provider.stable(), content=\"1\")\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

